# 🚀 Spacio

Spacio is a modern cloud storage and file management platform designed to help users securely store, organize, access, and manage their digital files through an intuitive and responsive interface.

The application provides secure user authentication, file uploading, categorization, search capabilities, storage insights, and seamless file management. Built using Next.js, TypeScript, Appwrite, Tailwind CSS, and Shadcn UI, Spacio demonstrates full-stack development concepts including authentication, cloud storage integration, database management, and responsive user experience design.

## Key Features

* Secure user authentication
* File upload and storage management
* Categorized file organization
* Advanced file search
* Storage analytics dashboard
* Download and management options
* Responsive modern interface
* Cloud-based backend powered by Appwrite

## Tech Stack

* Next.js
* TypeScript
* Appwrite
* Tailwind CSS
* Shadcn UI
* React

## Learning Outcomes

This project strengthened my understanding of:

* Full-stack web development
* Authentication and authorization
* Cloud storage systems
* Database integration
* Modern React and Next.js architecture
* Responsive UI/UX development
* Type-safe application development with TypeScript
